text: Ovsyanka () is a village in Krasnoyarsk Krai. The population at the 2010 census was 2228. ==Geography== Ovsyanka lies along the Yenisei River and is surrounded by forests. ==References== Category:Cities and towns in Krasnoyarsk Krai Category:Yeniseysk Governorate Category:Populated places on the Yenisei River
title: Ovsyanka, Krasnoyarsk Krai
